Pizza Funghi

For the pizza dough:

500 grams all-purpose flour
8 grams instant or active dry yeast
7 grams sea salt
338 grams warm water
13 grams olive oil
Semolina flour or cornmeal

For the sauce and toppings:

150 gr sliced mixed mushrooms
fresh thyme and oregano
sea salt, to taste
olive oil
fresh lemon juice
100 gr goat cheese, crumbled
50 gr shredded mozzarella cheese
finely chopped chives
